        <item>
          <versionCode>00</versionCode>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Puerto Rico Film, Television, and Theatre Production Act of 2018 </b></p> <p>This bill amends the Internal Revenue Code; with respect to rules that allow the expensing of certain costs of qualified film, television, and live theatrical productions; to: (1) apply the rules to Puerto Rico, and (2) extend the rules through 2021 for Puerto Rico. (Under current law, the rules apply through 2017 for productions with costs that include a specified amount of compensation for services performed in the United States.)</p>]]></text>
          <actionDate>2018-03-06</actionDate>
